data.description: One-of-a-kind custom mountain/lake retreat, luxurious yet comfortable, perfectly situated on an elevated 1.39 acres located on the Settlement side of the Reserve at Lake Keowee. As you enter the massive great room, you will  immediately be drawn to the wall of windows. Approximately 5400 square feet, 4 bedrooms, 4 ½ baths, this home has custom designed elements with attention to detail throughout. Stacked stone gas log fireplaces, vaulted pine paneled ceilings with reclaimed beams and cross beams, wood accents, 200-year-old reclaimed wood flooring, DaVinci roof, 2 1/2 car garage to accommodate your golf cart, custom iron work railings and slats, unique  decorative stone chimney cap,  generator, hydraulic elevator and so much more. This home is purposefully positioned to capture the views while retaining privacy. The MAIN level consists of an open living/dining floor plan with vaulted ceiling in great room, spacious kitchen with cozy dining nook, area for separate dining and room for your home office. In addition to the master suite, there is also the convenience of a guest ensuite perfect for family and guests. The kitchen includes Viking appliances, large granite island and gorgeous knotty alder cabinets with access to screened porch. The TERRACE level is ideal for entertaining with the bar/kitchen, rec room with gas log fireplace, two additional bedrooms, two full baths and plenty of storage. The custom bar/kitchen with concrete island, beverage refrigerator, dishwasher, ice machine and built in microwave has direct access to the open aired patio with maintenance free decking and cable railing. Take your golf cart down the beautiful paver path with abundance of boulders/retaining walls and hardscape features directly to the covered dock with seating area and Viking grill. Use the licensed pump from the lake for all your landscaping irrigation. Sports Membership can be upgraded to the Premier level. The Reserve at Lake Keowee offers a Jack Nicklaus Signature Golf Course, a par 3 practice facility with driving range and outdoor bar, Clubhouse with fine dining, pub area and wine bar, Fitness Center, Hiking Trails, 4 Har-Tru Clay Tennis Courts, Lakeside Resort-Style Pool and Cabana, Settlement Pool, 8 Pickleball Courts, Marina offering both slips and boat rentals, and Market great for lunch and select provisions. This gated community offers many activities including fitness classes, various social clubs, and a high-speed fiber-optic internet system in place. The Reserve at Lake Keowee is a full amenity lakefront golf community. Must see! Start making your memories today. Pre-inspected!
